{"tid":1999124,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[懷舊&本土情懷] 簡介＜A Summer's End - Hong Kong 1986＞","createTime":"2020-05-03T03:10:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-16T02:15:45.000Z","uid":191239,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"db16b98215bad7b1dec601a5a01467d7112f8e62","tid":1999124,"uid":191239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T03:10:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JVs5LV0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJVs5LV0.png&h=182841f5&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n官網：<a href=\"https://www.asummersend.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.asummersend.com%2F&d=5G%2Bx0n%2BFJXS0hP%2BJIuhjgom5R6Uo%2BMV3ZOx7awwfaZg%3D&h=35284c9e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.asummersend.com/</a><br />\nTLDR:<br />\n<br />\n1. 與其話係遊戲，其實係［<span style=\"color: pink;\">視覺小說</span>］<br />\n<br />\n2. 用1986年香港做舞台，無論音樂定畫風<br />\n<br />\n3. 重點：題材係<span style=\"color: pink;\">女同性戀</span><br />\n<br />\n4. 係一間加拿大game studio嘅處女作，目前只有<span style=\"color: red;\">英文版本</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oOxYnd2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoOxYnd2.png&h=406b6747&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n整體嚟講其實遊戲真係做得唔錯，由畫面到劇情都比到人新穎同衝擊。本身係比［<span style=\"color: pink;\">香港</span>］吸引左我買嚟玩，其次係<span style=\"color: violet;\">女同性戀</span>哩一個題材。哩兩個題材同時出現嘅機會唔多，令人好想知道故事點樣發展。<br />\n<br />\n先講下背景。作為一個香港玩家一入game就忍唔住去搵有冇一啲同香港不符嘅位，但我發現大部分都有好好還原。雖然我唔係果個年代嘅人，但一路玩我竟然愈來愈中意舊時香港。打冷呀紅van呀 哩啲，當然仲有標緻性嘅霓虹燈。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ydd8KJJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYdd8KJJ.png&h=43726e16&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n再講劇情部分。首先講明先目前只係得英文版本，以我英文只有中六程度嚟講查字典佔左遊戲時間大概10個鐘入面最少1/3。講係咁講但我睇劇情並冇唔舒服嘅地方，不過如果要一隻喺steam上面出嘅外國game整到全繁體中文，可能太苛刻。成隻遊戲圍繞住兩位女主角Sam同Michelle邂逅到相愛嘅故事，探討同性戀對傳統思想衝擊。喺哩一點上我覺得由對兩位主角心境嘅描寫，劇本係成功帶出到主題嘅。<span style=\"color: red;\">去到尾段作者仲借Sam把口暗示對香港前景係樂觀</span>。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KRgRHuV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKRgRHuV.png&h=977c280d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n自己從未試過玩同類型遊戲，不過同唔少人一樣我好睇重遊戲嘅畫風。以我所知真係得好少作品以[如果我冇估錯]香港8 90年代漫畫風格為題材去畫。<br />\n<br />\n以現代眼光睇哩隻遊戲嘅畫風，反而我覺得莫明嘅吸引。<br />\n好推薦大家去試下哩隻用80年代香港做舞台嘅遊戲，76蚊絕對值得一試。<br />\n最後都要利申翻自己好少寫評論，希望有咩講錯屌細力啲。有咩想知歡迎再問。<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c20fc81cd83020edec331de2701141f378390e85","tid":1999124,"uid":65429,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T03:11:42.000Z","msg":"有興趣 <br />\n但有中文先買"},{"pid":"d5bac6163181502eb3cc72493dcf168387dde582","tid":1999124,"uid":191239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T03:14:11.000Z","msg":"哩隻game出左無耐，可能因為無咩人識間studio所以無咩人討論<br />\n無我真心推薦大家去試下 大佬講香港喎 你估成日有<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔啱玩咪退<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9681ec7b1967f96a5255dbcc5b98fb08504086eb","tid":1999124,"uid":191239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c20fc81cd83020edec331de2701141f378390e85","tid":1999124,"uid":65429,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T03:11:42.000Z","msg":"有興趣 <br />\n但有中文先買"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T03:16:06.000Z","msg":"自己down左先知得英文<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不過頂硬上 曬左唔少時間查字典 當學下英文<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd401a77e4cd38cf258270a50ce5f2ac2b79882a","tid":1999124,"uid":49456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T03:40:14.000Z","msg":"LM留意"},{"pid":"06e1741f5cc4ec1fe36aa25052bc6a42356712be","tid":1999124,"uid":126862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T01:49:36.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"fe19356b3e8d02c8603308ee0dfae2c667f6002d","tid":1999124,"uid":41414,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-0